Comment.Text: File Reader 10 (+1 ref) channels, 512 Hz, 32 samples per block Hand Motor Imagery session
Spatial filter We compute the surface Laplacians around C3 and C4.
Topographies We display the alpha band power on a 2D and a 3D map
Temporal filtering We remove the 50 Hz noise with a notch filter and select only the frequency range between 1 and 40 Hz.
Spectral analysis The decimation downsamples the signal from 512 Hz to 64 Hz. The spectrum is thus computed up to 32Hz
